[
    {
        "text": "Face it. Unless you like kicking puppies and smacking babies,...",
        "startTime": 3075,
        "endTime": 7225,
        "slowStartTime": 4762,
        "slowEndTime": 11063
    },
    {
        "text": "...firing someone is not pleasant.",
        "startTime": 7559,
        "endTime": 9337,
        "slowStartTime": 11489,
        "slowEndTime": 14230
    },
    {
        "text": "The person doing the firing doesn't sleep well night before.",
        "startTime": 9856,
        "endTime": 12949,
        "slowStartTime": 14934,
        "slowEndTime": 19648
    },
    {
        "text": "They know it must be done, but often don't know quite what to do or say.",
        "startTime": 13375,
        "endTime": 17149,
        "slowStartTime": 20213,
        "slowEndTime": 25948
    },
    {
        "text": "What Do I Say?",
        "startTime": 18024,
        "endTime": 18924,
        "slowStartTime": 27186,
        "slowEndTime": 28611
    },
    {
        "text": "The best way to tell somebody is to just directly tell them.",
        "startTime": 19663,
        "endTime": 22826,
        "slowStartTime": 29644,
        "slowEndTime": 34464
    },
    {
        "text": "\"We've decided to make a change.\"",
        "startTime": 23349,
        "endTime": 24754,
        "slowStartTime": 35173,
        "slowEndTime": 37356
    },
    {
        "text": "Or, \"It's not working out, and we're going to need to let you go.\"",
        "startTime": 24998,
        "endTime": 28349,
        "slowStartTime": 37647,
        "slowEndTime": 42748
    },
    {
        "text": "People already know when a relationship is not going well,...",
        "startTime": 29085,
        "endTime": 31915,
        "slowStartTime": 43777,
        "slowEndTime": 48097
    },
    {
        "text": "...so most of the time they are expecting it.",
        "startTime": 32262,
        "endTime": 34231,
        "slowStartTime": 48543,
        "slowEndTime": 51572
    },
    {
        "text": "When Do I Say It?",
        "startTime": 35104,
        "endTime": 36001,
        "slowStartTime": 52806,
        "slowEndTime": 54227
    },
    {
        "text": "Not on a Friday, if you can help it.",
        "startTime": 36724,
        "endTime": 38536,
        "slowStartTime": 55236,
        "slowEndTime": 58029
    },
    {
        "text": "When you fire someone at the end of a week,...",
        "startTime": 39077,
        "endTime": 40863,
        "slowStartTime": 58765,
        "slowEndTime": 61519
    },
    {
        "text": "...you sentence them to two days, Saturday and Sunday, of self-torment.",
        "startTime": 41105,
        "endTime": 45137,
        "slowStartTime": 61807,
        "slowEndTime": 67931
    },
    {
        "text": "By releasing them into the world at the beginning of the week,...",
        "startTime": 45811,
        "endTime": 48342,
        "slowStartTime": 68866,
        "slowEndTime": 72738
    },
    {
        "text": "...they may actually have the time to make a few phone calls or set up a meeting or two.",
        "startTime": 48687,
        "endTime": 52795,
        "slowStartTime": 73180,
        "slowEndTime": 79418
    },
    {
        "text": "What Do We Do After I Say It?",
        "startTime": 53935,
        "endTime": 55815,
        "slowStartTime": 81053,
        "slowEndTime": 83948
    },
    {
        "text": "If they want to talk, listen to them.",
        "startTime": 56645,
        "endTime": 58574,
        "slowStartTime": 85117,
        "slowEndTime": 88086
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't argue, don't get defensive,...",
        "startTime": 58897,
        "endTime": 60717,
        "slowStartTime": 88496,
        "slowEndTime": 91300
    },
    {
        "text": "...and don't feel that you have to explain or justify your decision.",
        "startTime": 60957,
        "endTime": 64147,
        "slowStartTime": 91586,
        "slowEndTime": 96445
    },
    {
        "text": "You are the one in control.",
        "startTime": 64733,
        "endTime": 66075,
        "slowStartTime": 97249,
        "slowEndTime": 99337
    },
    {
        "text": "It is very helpful to anticipate their questions in advance.",
        "startTime": 66615,
        "endTime": 69637,
        "slowStartTime": 100072,
        "slowEndTime": 104680
    },
    {
        "text": "That way, you can put all the information in writing.",
        "startTime": 70087,
        "endTime": 72720,
        "slowStartTime": 105280,
        "slowEndTime": 109305
    },
    {
        "text": "After you answer their questions,...",
        "startTime": 73313,
        "endTime": 74770,
        "slowStartTime": 110120,
        "slowEndTime": 112380
    },
    {
        "text": "...simply give them the memo explaining what you have just told them.",
        "startTime": 75099,
        "endTime": 78420,
        "slowStartTime": 112799,
        "slowEndTime": 117855
    }
]